How to Install gh (GitHub CLI)

## For Ubuntu / Debian (Linux)

sudo apt update
sudo apt install gh

##For macOS (with Homebrew)

/bin/bash -c "$(curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Homebrew/install/HEAD/install.sh)"  #for the first time installation only

## Add Homebrew to your PATH

echo >> ~/.bash_profile
echo 'eval "$(/opt/homebrew/bin/brew shellenv)"' >> ~/.bash_profile
eval "$(/opt/homebrew/bin/brew shellenv)"

brew install gh   # Install GitHub CLI (gh) using Homebrew


## After Install: Authenticate

gh auth login 
